    "body": "`useMemo` is being called after the `loading`/`error` early returns. That violates the Rules of Hooks because the first render returns before calling `useMemo`, and later renders call an extra hook, which can throw \"Rendered more hooks than during the previous render\". Move the derived `confirmRate`/`grouped` calculations (including `useMemo`) above any conditional returns so hooks are called unconditionally.",
